vernac_cmds: intros HT P Q R S T U HPTQ HRTS HQUR HNC HCong1 HCong2.
assert (Hc1 : Bet V P R) by (unfold Midpoint in *; spliter; Between).
assert (Hc2 : Bet Q U R) by (unfold BetS in *; spliter; Between).
destruct (inner_pasch V Q R P U) as [W [HPWQ HUWV]]; Col; clear Hc1; clear Hc2.
intro; treat_equalities; apply HNC; unfold BetS in *; spliter; assert_cols; ColR.
apply HNC; apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; assert_cols; ColR.
destruct (HT P V U W Q) as [X [Y [HPVX [HPUY HXQY]]]]; Between.
assert (HPar : Par_strict Q S P R).
assert_diffs; unfold BetS in *; spliter; apply l12_17 with T; try split; Cong; Between.
assert (HTS : TS Q S P Y).
assert (P <> R) by (intro; treat_equalities; apply par_strict_distinct in HPar; spliter; Col).
assert (P <> X) by (intro; treat_equalities; apply par_strict_distinct in HPar; spliter; Col).
apply par_strict_symmetry; apply par_strict_col_par_strict with R; Col.
unfold BetS in *; unfold Midpoint in *; spliter; assert_diffs; assert_cols; ColR.
assert (Q = Y) by (apply l6_21 with Q S X Q; try (intro; treat_equalities); Col).
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; apply l6_21 with Q P R Q; Col.
treat_equalities; unfold BetS in *; spliter; Col.
assert (P <> R) by (intro; treat_equalities; apply par_strict_distinct in HPar; spliter; Col).
assert (P <> V) by (intro; treat_equalities; apply par_strict_distinct in HPar; spliter; Col).
assert (P <> X) by (intro; treat_equalities; apply par_strict_distinct in HPar; spliter; Col).
apply l12_6; apply par_strict_right_comm; apply par_strict_col_par_strict with R; Col.
destruct HTS as [Hc1 [Hc2 [I [HCol HBet]]]]; clear Hc1; clear Hc2; exists I.
assert (HPUI : Col P U I) by (assert_cols; ColR).
elim HPUI; clear HPUI; intro HPUI; Col.
elim HPUI; clear HPUI; intro HPUI; exfalso.
assert (HFalse : TS Q S P U).
split; try (exists I; split; Col; Between).
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; apply l6_21 with S Q R Q; Col.
treat_equalities; unfold BetS in *; spliter; intuition.
apply l9_9 in HFalse; apply HFalse.
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; assert_diffs; assert_cols; apply l9_19 with Q; Col.
assert (HFalse : TS P R I U).
split; try (intro; apply HPar; exists I; Col).
split; try (exists P; split; Col; Between).
unfold BetS in *; spliter; apply l6_21 with P R Q U; Col.
treat_equalities; unfold BetS in *; spliter; intuition.
apply l9_9 in HFalse; apply HFalse.
apply l12_6; apply par_strict_right_comm; apply par_strict_col_par_strict with S; Par; Col.
intro; treat_equalities; apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; apply HNC; assert_cols; ColR.
assert (HPar':= HPar); apply par_strict_distinct in HPar.
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; assert_diffs; assert_cols; apply l9_19 with R; Col.
split; try (intro; treat_equalities; apply par_strict_not_col_3 in HPar; apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; assert_cols; Col).
apply l6_21 with S Q R Q; Col.
treat_equalities; unfold BetS in *; spliter; intuition.
assert (HTS : TS Q R S I).
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; apply BetSEq in HPUI; spliter; assert_diffs.
assert_cols; repeat split; try (exists U; Col).
intro; apply par_strict_not_col_4 in HPar; apply HPar; ColR.
apply par_not_col_strict with P; Col; try (intro; apply par_strict_not_col_3 in HPar; Col).
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; assert_diffs; spliter; apply l12_17 with T; try split; Cong; Between.
apply l9_9 in HFalse; exfalso; apply HFalse.
apply BetSEq in HPTQ; apply BetSEq in HRTS; apply BetSEq in HQUR; spliter; apply l9_19 with Q; Col.
apply par_strict_not_col_4 in HPar; split; Col.
unfold TS in HTS; spliter; assert_diffs; repeat split; elim HSQI; Between.
assert (HFalse := HTS); unfold TS in HTS; spliter; assert_diffs; repeat split; Col; intro; treat_equalities; assert (HTS := not_two_sides_id S Q R); Col.
